## Amendment (2026-04-26): policy_resolution.json schema extension

Per the F-B14 oracle resolution (see comment on bd-3ix), `policy_resolution.json` now carries an additional `compile_knobs` section:

```json
{
  "compile_knobs": {
    "global":     { /* CompileKnobValues */ },
    "bounds":     { /* CompileKnobBounds */ },
    "locks":      { /* KnobLockSet */ },
    "overrides":  { /* CompileKnobOverrides */ },
    "provenance": { /* per-knob ConstraintProvenance — PolicySource + EvidenceRefs */ }
  }
}
```

`PolicySource` enumerates the legal origins: `TargetDefault | ProfileDefault | CompileRequestOverride | HintBundle | Calibration | RepairProposal(RepairProposalId)`. Every resolved value must trace back to one of those.

This is part of F-B14's T-B14.7 deliverable but lives architecturally inside F-B0's `ResolvedCompilePolicy` emission. Coordinate with T-B14.7 when implementing.

